Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:23.99,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur1\c&HCCF2F4&\pos(1146.019,336)\frz270\fs75\fad(830,0)}交 错 的      关 系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:23.99,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1a&H9f\blur13\frz270\fs75\pos(1146.019,336)\fad(0,830)}交 错 的      关 系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君月君？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前 我和与一受到了姓柊那帮家伙的讯问
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被问及的是 在那个战场上究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你们是怎么回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你命令的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正确的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样对优保密下去也是正确的做法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们口中的伙伴只是漂亮话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在背后却在利用优的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:11.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会为了妹妹留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍受你们的恶心 装出同伴的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂君月 你说得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱娅是为了从上级那里保护优才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的 三三
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与一也是同样的意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我觉得筱娅你们是为了优君才选择保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能对你们说清楚 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.24,0:05:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我的内心是想要成为同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等这个训练结束 就把一切都说清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光是优的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我们大家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快来把优按住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.42,0:06:13.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是正式和鬼接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会生下这样的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不把「终结的炽天使」给杀掉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.17,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是恶魔之子…优
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 过来吧 优
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你去个好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你必须要死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.91,0:07:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为你逃走了 大家才会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩溃吧 优
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会因为这样就暴走的 阿朱罗丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事情等着我去做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我和他约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小优
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起来保护家人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.79,0:07:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为你需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我一定会去救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为赢了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么和你战斗我已经了如指掌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别虚张声势 你这个被父母抛弃的死恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要米迦需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要红莲和筱娅他们需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.51,0:08:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就算是恶魔也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 感觉比之前更强了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你这种有所觉悟样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想伤害你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.75,0:08:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.51,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你 阿朱罗丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起去救米迦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对我有什么好处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会成为你的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孤身一人是很痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被任何人需要 是很难受的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.43,0:08:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深有体会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会要成为我的同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成我给你们添麻烦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算是回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.77,0:09:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你可是大闹了一场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 这并非是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过果然很累人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君月的修行就放到下周再做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 开什么玩笑 我马上就要做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 马上的话不太想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 连你这家伙也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.95,0:09:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有被鬼伤到内心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多亏了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不是孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简而言之就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类遵循自身的欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,染指禁忌研究所诞生出的缺陷品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要看了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想就能一目了然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 刚才那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是让那种东西得以实用化…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类最终还是在把「终结的炽天使」推向武器化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.08,0:10:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个不容忽视的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:11:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个研究不是因为克鲁鲁大人毁了白夜教之后停止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八年前我阻止了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持有「终结的炽天使」因子的孩子 都由我亲手杀光了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验体全被杀光了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前就应该说过了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}那么为何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,研究能得到如此进展
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明除了百夜教 不存在任何组织能将研究进展到这步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是之前管理存在失误的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁鲁 这可是严重的责任问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住口 雷斯特·卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是在向我挑衅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你无法胜任的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会代替你坐上日本的王位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别得寸进尺 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才两百年左右能有什么变化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且在实力上我更…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}好了好了 您二位别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过克鲁鲁大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上人类的确是在将其武器化
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要以怎样的对策应对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本方针不变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出动本队 将日本帝鬼军消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期待你的成果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 费里德·巴特利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身后的孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把米迦勒带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且刚才的影像…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是打算陷害我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.05,0:12:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没法杀了我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所掌握的情报也许就会流落到上位始祖会那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 放走小优的事要是暴露的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会受到处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是共享秘密的同伴咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来握个手 克鲁鲁·采佩西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克鲁…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君月君 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 筱娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.13,0:14:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和我刚才一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也许情况有些糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有被鬼夺取身体的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那该怎么办好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请做好最坏的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拼命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从我吧 鬼箱王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会服从弱者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.13,0:14:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体已经为我所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,崩溃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不太好 病情进展太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实食物快没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,储备粮食连三天都支撑不住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要舍弃这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 决定明早出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转移未来的准备还没……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍弃未来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.91,0:15:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 君月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是有责任的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.33,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天必须一边保护幸存下来的孩子一边转移
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界没有美好到能让我们带着病人移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是为了你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑 那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.21,0:16:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是未来这么拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说不想拖累哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.34,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为自己无法动弹所以没法亲自动手…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你无法做到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我们动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 君月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开门 君月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从阳台绕过去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想成为哥哥的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你 杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不想看到哥哥因为我而痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.15,0:17:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里你想要让自己获得解放
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我要遭遇这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明我也还只是个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能在这里杀了妹妹的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能卸下这个重担的话 不就能轻松了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是这么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样的 君月士方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无需忍耐 解放自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我解脱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.79,0:18:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.29,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我所期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后能听我一言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.96,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近认识了一个奇怪的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.27,0:18:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是个让人咬牙切齿的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.38,0:18:31.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼了命想去救 明明没有血缘关系的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真是个笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.75,0:18:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有理由输给那种笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且你还是和我有血缘的至亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我下手杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.88,0:18:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我自行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 鬼箱王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君月君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:30.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你为什么攻击我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你 究竟谁强有必要决出一下不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.54,0:19:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 我就能一直比你强了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是要来真的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.05,0:19:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}喂 住手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擅自战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很有趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 阿朱罗丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.72,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展开 阿朱罗观音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭鼻子哦 君月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始进入鬼箱前的「九个倒计时」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼箱王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二  三  四
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 喂 不要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个 绝对是什么可怕的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.14,0:20:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉非常地不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个笨蛋 直觉倒挺准的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这次倒是被他的笨蛋举止给救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.72,0:20:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 和笨蛋是没法打交道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真敢说啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:20:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.28,0:21:01.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}真是的 大家好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筱娅 刚刚的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两人都使出了通常无法使用的特殊能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与一也没有进行修行就学会了具现化
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲中校是怎么聚集到这些人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.33,0:21:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 这到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:23.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有谁把那三人过去的资料给消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.59,0:21:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有红莲中校了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中校是真的打算和军部上层翻脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那么单纯的事情倒好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人体实验
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有和吸血鬼的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.26,0:21:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉有什么很不妙的事情要发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.67,0:23:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下回 终结的炽天使
